description: Retrieves a list of events that occurred during a specific time in a space. You can use these events to audit user and system activity in a space. For more information, see Monitoring in the Amazon CodeCatalyst User Guide.

parameters.name: startTime
parameters.description: The date and time when you want to start retrieving events, in coordinated universal time (UTC) timestamp format as specified in RFC 3339.

parameters.name: endTime
parameters.description: The time after which you do not want any events retrieved, in coordinated universal time (UTC) timestamp format as specified in RFC 3339.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token returned from a call to this API to indicate the next batch of results to return, if any.

nested_items.name: items
nested_items.description: Information about each event retrieved in the list.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The system-generated unique ID of the event.

nested_items.name: eventName
nested_items.description: The name of the event.

nested_items.name: eventType
nested_items.description: The type of the event.

nested_items.name: eventCategory
nested_items.description: The category for the event.

nested_items.name: eventSource
nested_items.description: The source of the event.

nested_items.name: eventTime
nested_items.description: The time the event took place, in coordinated universal time (UTC) timestamp format as specified in RFC 3339.

nested_items.name: operationType
nested_items.description: The type of the event.

nested_items.name: userIdentity
nested_items.description: The system-generated unique ID of the user whose actions are recorded in the event.

nested_items.name: userType
nested_items.description: The role assigned to the user in a Amazon CodeCatalyst space or project when the event occurred.

nested_items.name: principalId
nested_items.description: The ID of the Amazon CodeCatalyst service principal.

nested_items.name: userName
nested_items.description: The display name of the user in Amazon CodeCatalyst.

nested_items.name: awsAccountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account number of the user in Amazon Web Services, if any.

nested_items.name: projectInformation
nested_items.description: Information about the project where the event occurred.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the project in the space.

nested_items.name: projectId
nested_items.description: The system-generated unique ID of the project.

nested_items.name: requestId
nested_items.description: The system-generated unique ID of the request.

nested_items.name: requestPayload
nested_items.description: Information about the payload of the request.

nested_items.name: contentType
nested_items.description: The type of content in the event payload.

nested_items.name: data
nested_items.description: The data included in the event payload.

nested_items.name: responsePayload
nested_items.description: Information about the payload of the response, if any.

nested_items.name: contentType
nested_items.description: The type of content in the event payload.

nested_items.name: data
nested_items.description: The data included in the event payload.

nested_items.name: errorCode
nested_items.description: The code of the error, if any.

nested_items.name: sourceIpAddress
nested_items.description: The IP address of the user whose actions are recorded in the event.

nested_items.name: userAgent
nested_items.description: The user agent whose actions are recorded in the event.
